            "description": "As the first Iranian application to alert drivers about speed cameras in their ways, I developed both client and server side of this project. SpeedCam120 reached 11.5K users in less than 2 years. in SpeedCam120 drivers can get notified if they are driving with higher speed than the speed cameras in their way. They can also add camera to their app\u2019s database or even send it to the main database, which of course needs other users validation to get into the update list, to prevent fake data getting into database and ruining user experience and trust in app. This was a challenge which I solved by defining a parameter that a number of user must define a given point or 50m around it as a speed camera, so no speed cam with less than 3 unique users validation was marked as validated cam. ",
